# API

Every API request must:

- handle loading
- handle errors
- handle timeout
- handle retries
- handle cancellation
- prevent duplicate requests
- prevent race conditions
- cache where appropriate
- invalidate cache correctly

Never fetch the same data twice unnecessarily.

Use optimistic updates only when appropriate.

Validate every API response.

Never assume response shape.
